visit

public boolean visit(JsFor x,
                     JsContext ctx)
This is essentially a hacked-up version of JsFor.traverse to account for flow control differing from visitation order. It resets lastFile and lastLine before the condition and increment expressions in the for loop so that location data will be recorded correctly.
